-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"af090494-ad44-43c9-ba50-5018ce99aa39\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/hdr_vault_hdri/11200_part5.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469274\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"af090494-ad44-43c9-ba50-5018ce99aa39\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"hdrVault_preview.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/hdrVault_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285928513&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=387\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469242/hdrVault_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285928513&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"970\" data-width=\"1903\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608141701\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"hdrVault_preview.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"b13667a1-4ec9-4b2a-a316-187a3076ff19\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/hdrVault_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285928513&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=774 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/hdrVault_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285928513&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=387 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"HDRVault-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>HDR Vault is the work of Philip Modin. They are in the public domain and have been pre-converted by Leo Frison.</p><h2 id=\"HDRVault-How-to\">How-to</h2><p>This resource is designed to work with RenderMan's&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki.pixar.com/display/RFM22/Preset+Browser+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\">Preset Browser</a>.</p><p>Drag the contents of the&nbsp;folder into your <strong>Asset Library &gt; EnvironmentMaps</strong> folder. The files are organized by category and can be easily searched in your preset browser.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"ba8786e0-e629-466f-8bdb-6595039e4626\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Make sure to transfer the installation&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki.pixar.com/display/RFM22/Preset+Browser+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>RenderManAssetLibrary</strong></a> folder to a location with full writing privileges.</p></div></div><p>Once you transfer the Materials folder and move your Asset Library into a different location, it is important to tell Maya through the preferences that you want to use the new path.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711517&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469242/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711517&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"622\" data-width=\"776\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469292\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"preset-browser-add-library.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"c11cf24c-08e8-444b-9844-785f2cb35d8b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711517&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=776&amp;height=622 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/preset-browser-add-library.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711517&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=609 1x\" /></span><p>Or you can create a new environment variable in your Maya.env file, which&nbsp;will make sure you are always pointing to the right folder:</p><p><code>RMAN_ASSET_LIBRARY = /My/Folder/Example/RenderManAssetLibrary</code></p><p /><hr /><h3 id=\"HDRVault-Copyright\">Copyright</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Public Domain. Free of known copyright restrictions.</a></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"cc-zero.png\" width=\"127\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=127&amp;height=44\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469242/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"142\" data-width=\"403\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469271\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"cc-zero.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"98ba6b05-ebe1-47d9-9d1d-0f6f7847769f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=254&amp;height=88 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/cc-zero.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285711039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=127&amp;height=44 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" width=\"100\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285710703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608469242/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285710703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"100\" data-width=\"100\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608469265\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608469242\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"e0958aa9-3709-4551-8e1c-f22162f14484\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285710703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608469242/RenderManUniversity_logo_Small.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285710703&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=100&amp;height=100 1x\" /></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
